<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٥٥٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5093">أَبُو نُعَيْمٍ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6739">هَمَّامٌ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ </a>قَالَ <span class="c2">«سَأَلْتُ أَنَسًا هَلْ خَضَبَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ لَا إِنَّمَا كَانَ شَيْءٌ فِي صُدْغَيْهِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>